Name: acute cervicitis
Definition: A cervicitis that is characterized by onset within the past 1 - 3 days.

Name: chronic cervicitis
Definition: A cervicitis that is present for weeks or more.

Name: obsolete mitral valve syphilitic endocarditis
Definition: A cervicitis that is present for weeks or more.

Name: obsolete syphilitic endocarditis
Definition: A cervicitis that is present for weeks or more.

Name: endocervicitis
Definition: A cervicitis that is located_in the endocervix.
